title: What Actually Happens At A Dog Convention | UnConventional
description: In this video, Max Fosh attends a dog convention to see what actually happens at these events. He interviews dog owners, checks out the various stalls, and participates in dog-related activities.
summary: Max Fosh attends a dog convention to explore what goes on at these events and interact with dog owners and activities.
payoff: The humor in this video comes from Max's deadpan delivery and interactions with the dog owners and activities at the convention. The absurdity of some of the activities and the over-the-top enthusiasm of the attendees add to the comedic effect.
